" ======= 引号 && 括号自动匹配 ======= "
:inoremap ( ()<ESC>i
:inoremap ) <c-r>=ClosePair(')')<CR>
:inoremap { {}<ESC>i
:inoremap } <c-r>=ClosePair('}')<CR>
:inoremap [ []<ESC>i
:inoremap ] <c-r>=ClosePair(']')<CR>
":inoremap < <><ESC>i
":inoremap > <C-R>=ClosePair('>')<CR>
:inoremap " ""<ESC>i
":inoremap ' ''<ESC>i
" :inoremap ` ``<ESC>i
:inoremap $ $$<ESC>i
function ClosePair(char)
    if getline('.')[col('.') - 1] == a:char
        return "\<Right>"
    else
        return a:char
    endif
endf
" ======= 引号 && 括号自动匹配 ======= "

"===============================自动补全===============================
imap <c-\> <c-p>
" c-j自动补全，当补全菜单打开时，c-j,k上下选择
" f:文件名补全，l:行补全，d:字典补全，]:tag补全,t thesaurus
